OL,5, Half a century after Slade recorded    
OL,6, their massive hit single Merry Xmas    
OL,7, Everybody, Noddy Holder said strangers 
OL,8, still ask him to shout his "It's       
OL,9, Christmas" catchphrase.                
OL,11,FIn an interview with the BBC, the      
OL,12,F77-year-old said the words were written
OL,13,Fafter a trip to the pub.               
OL,15,FThe melody was taken from a song he    
OL,16,Fwrote and discarded six years          
OL,17,Fpreviously.                            
OL,19,FBut the recording of the number one    
OL,20,Fsingle was far from easy.              
